### Review API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1

# ============ PUBLIC ROUTES (No Auth Required) ============

### 1. Create a new review (replace productId with actual product ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "YOUR_PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
  "reviewerName": "John Doe",
  "reviewerEmail": "john@example.com",
  "rating": 5,
  "title": "Excellent product!",
  "comment": "This product exceeded my expectations. Great quality and fast delivery!"
}

### 2. Create another review without email and title
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "YOUR_PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
  "reviewerName": "Jane Smith",
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Good product overall. Would recommend to others looking for quality items."
}

### 3. Create review with minimum rating
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "YOUR_PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
  "reviewerName": "Bob Wilson",
  "rating": 2,
  "comment": "Product was okay but not what I expected. Delivery was late."
}

### 4. Get all reviews for a product (replace with actual product ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/product/YOUR_PRODUCT_ID_HERE

# ============ ADMIN ROUTES ============

### 5. Get all reviews (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/admin/all

### 6. Get pending reviews (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/admin/pending

### 7. Get single review (replace with actual review ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/YOUR_REVIEW_ID_HERE

### 8. Update a review (replace with actual review ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reviews/YOUR_REVIEW_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Updated my review - the product grew on me!"
}

### 9. Toggle review approval (replace with actual review ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/reviews/admin/toggle-approval/YOUR_REVIEW_ID_HERE

### 10. Delete a review (replace with actual review ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reviews/YOUR_REVIEW_ID_HERE
